function response(room, msg, sender, isGroupChat, replier, imageDB, packageName) {

if (msg.indexOf("/총검색")==0) { //총검색이라고 입력을 받았을때

var keyw = msg.substr(5); //총검색 총이름 중 총이름만 빼온다

var rst = org.jsoup.Jsoup.connect("http://www.shootersclub.co.kr/goods/goods_search.php? keyword="+keyw).get().select("div.search-page").select("strong").get(0).text();

var rna = org.jsoup.Jsoup.connect("http://www.shootersclub.co.kr/goods/goods_search.php?keyword="+keyw).get().select("div.search-page").select("strong").select("em").get(0).text();

var pro = org.jsoup.Jsoup.connect("http://www.shootersclub.co.kr/goods/goods_search.php?keyword="+keyw).get().select("div.list").select("strong");

var imgbase = org.jsoup.Jsoup.connect("http://www.shootersclub.co.kr/goods/goods_search.php?keyword="+keyw).get().select("div.thumbnail").select("meta[property=og:image]").attr("middle"); //사용 안함

//1태그

try {

var pro1n = pro.get(0).text();

var pro1p = pro.get(1).text();

}catch (e){

var pro1n = " "

var pro1p = " "

}

//2태그

try {

var pro2n = pro.get(2).text();

var pro2p = pro.get(3).text();

}catch (e){

var pro2n = " "

var pro2p = " "

}

//3태그

try {

var pro3n = pro.get(4).text();

var pro3p = pro.get(5).text();

}catch (e) {

var pro3n = " "

var pro3p = " "

}

//4태그

try {

var pro4n = pro.get(6).text();

var pro4p = pro.get(7).text();

}catch (e){

var pro4n = " "

var pro4p = " "

}

​

replier.reply(pro1n+pro1p+"\n"+pro2n+pro2p+"\n"+pro3n+pro3p+"\n"+pro4n+pro4p);

​

}

}
